{"tid":2442100,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"17歲拒絕1000萬美元支票 只有詹皇做得到","createTime":"2021-03-11T06:59:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T08:05:37.000Z","uid":150100,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f44d7744f6aa9688be3f3d419974ca81b3ceafba","tid":2442100,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:59:08.000Z","msg":"湖人一哥詹姆士(LeBron James)不只場上表現一把罩，就連場外副業也經營得有聲有色，今天還成為美國商業雜誌《快速公司》封面人物，暢談自己的理財觀念。<br />\n<br />\n詹姆士自爆：「當我還是1個17歲的孩子時，我過著一般人的生活，但當時Reebok拿了1張1000萬美元(約2.9億台幣)的支票給我，條件是我永遠不能和Nike或adidas洽談，說實話，我不清楚當時為何我沒有接受那張1000萬美元的支票，但我一向是1個會想得很遠的人。」<br />\n<br />\n雖然錯失1000萬美元，但詹姆士卻換來在Nike呼風喚雨的地位，更打造出屬於自己的商業王國，經營的副業超多元，跨足影視、服飾、餐飲、房地產等領域，且每項副業都十分成功，凸顯詹姆士獨到的投資眼光。(陳雍仁／綜合報導)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&quot;17歲拒絕1000萬美元支票 只有詹皇做得到 ｜ 蘋果新聞網 ｜ 蘋果日報&quot; <a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/sports/20210309/PS7HIRD4BFHADEBZIKAKV6PTAA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20210309%2FPS7HIRD4BFHADEBZIKAKV6PTAA%2F&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHRnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=e1a58e1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20210309%2FPS7HIRD4BFHADEBZIKAKV6PTAA%2F&h=4092a139\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/sports/20210309/PS7HIRD4BFHADEBZIKAKV6PTAA/</a><br />\n<br />\n霸氣到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0149e67c0951e337b0364607e1bb9cff513750ec","tid":2442100,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T07:00:57.000Z","msg":"之後果陣佢收咗5000萬支票"},{"pid":"76bfb53eb923e02d487d68794de98977f14d7b7e","tid":2442100,"uid":134421,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T07:04:04.000Z","msg":"On9先會簽reebok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打籃球冇得著jordan真係恥辱"},{"pid":"2497936b750